article.headline: Pierce and Allocco score 22 points apiece as Princeton defeats Bucknell 85-71
article.description: — Caden Pierce and Matt Allocco scored 22 points apiece in Princeton's 85-71 win against Bucknell on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Pierce and Allocco score 22 points apiece as Princeton defeats Bucknell 85-71
article.story: LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Caden Pierce and Matt Allocco scored 22 points apiece in Princeton's 85-71 win against Bucknell on Wednesday night. Xaivian Lee had 15 points and finished 6 of 9 from the field for the Tigers (7-0) The Bison (2-7) were led by Jack Forrest, who recorded 21 points and six rebounds. Josh Bascoe added 14 points and six assists for Bucknell. In addition, Noah Williamson finished with 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
